\f0\fs24 \cf0 The region is wealthy and prosperous, as compared to bordering regions like Wesshewen, Ilyushan, Krbshanana, the Forgh and even Aranzen.  As compared to our own time, it is closer to subsistence economics, relying on inter-locking systems of institutional centralization and planning, and small-scale barter and markets, with occasional larger-scale auctions and commodities markets.\
